<article>
  <ul class="playlist-list">
    {% for playlist in playlists -%}
      <li>
        <a class="big-text playlist-link" href="{{playlist.url}}" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
          {{playlist.name}}
        </a>
        <div class="playlist-img" style="--image:url({{playlist.image}})"></div>
        <br>
        <small>{{playlist.description | safe}}</small>
      </li>
    {% endfor %}
  </ul>
  
  <p class="big-text">
    These playlists help me go through my day-to-day life and to focus on literally anything. They are constant work-in-progress.
  </p>

  <p class="big-text">
    this is my goto for when im studying / concentrating on somthing.
  </p>
  <br>

  <iframe style="border-radius:12px" src="https://open.spotify.com/embed/playlist/0vvXsWCC9xrXsKd4FyS8kM?utm_source=generator&theme=0" width="100%" height="352" frameBorder="0" allowfullscreen="" allow="autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; fullscreen; picture-in-picture" loading="lazy"></iframe>

  <p class="big-text">More will be added soon 😁.</p>
